\mt1 2 Korin  
\mt2 Naoa it…ôm tatol k…ôiu lan it…ôm Pol t…ôm…ôte tuw…®n k…ôm i…ôfak m…®n ik…®n Korin  
\imt1 N…ôghat…ôn …ôku…ôk…®r r…ôha naoa u 2 Korin  
\ip \bd ?Pah t…ôm…ôte naoa u?\bd* Aposol Pol t…ôm…ôte naoa u.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm pah?\bd* T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm nim…ôfak r…ôha Korin, ne i…ôfak m…®n r…ôha profens Akaea.  
\ip \bd ?N…ômeg…ôh…ôn tahro nulan nian t…ôm…ôte?\bd* Pol t…®n…ôm…ôte r…ôk…®s naoa k…®s…®l mahl-ip…ôn k…ôm nim…ôfak r…ôha Korin. Inu naoa it…ôm tatol kuw…®t lan. M…ôto naoa it…ôm tatol kiti…ôh, ne naoa it…ôm tatol k…®s…®l, ilau k…ômiak…ô. Naoa it…ôm tatol k…ôiu, inu 1 Korin, k…ôn e naoa u in t…ôm…ôghat …ôskas…®k k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô okot…ôg-…ôtuat…®p-in nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhalat, k…ôn in t…ôm…ôg…ôtun m…®n ilat e nat…®mnat p…®s…®n m…®n neen. Ilat tep…ôt e nim…ôfak kot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha Pol it…ôm t…ôm…ôte e naoa 1 Korin. M…ôto neen …ôh-ik…®n, ilat koat…ôn m…ôm…ô Pol in s…ôn…ôm…ô et…ôm-iasol, k…ôn t…ôs…ôtuat…®p…ôn m…ôm…ô in ot…ôghat min n…ôhlan. K…ôn ilat koat…ôn m…ôm…ô in tatol w…ôk r…ôhan o nos…ôn …ôm m…ôni.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte naoa u o naka?\bd* Pol in t…ôm…ôte naoa u mat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô in aposol kit, k…ôn Uhg…®n in t…ômos-ip…ôn w…ôk u k…ôm in, k…ôn t…ôtuat…®p …ôm m…ôm…ô in ot…ôghat n…ôhlan k…ôm ilat. K…ôn in tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…ôn-i…ôhau n…ôg…ôtun eiueiu…ô m…®n it…ôm koatat…®g Korin.  
\c 1  
\s1 Pol t…ôm…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm ilat  
\m
\v 1 Io Pol, it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…®t…ôpun e n…ôwian m…ôm…ô io aposol r…ôha Kristo Iesu, iat…ôte naoa u it…®mlau pi…ôtat Timoti. Naoa u tat…®mn…ô k…ôm it…ômat, nim…ôfak r…ôha Uhg…®n …ôp…ôh Korin, ne i…ôfak m…®n ilat rafin …ôp…ôh ik…®n Akaea.  
\v 2 P…ôs Uhg…®n Tata r…ôhatat ne I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu Kristo, okuawte-in n…ôw…®r…ôn ne n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn k…ôm it…ômat.   
\s1 Uhg…®n it…ôm tatol kep…®n net…ômim  
\p
\v 3 P…ôs kot…ônwiwi Uhg…®n, u in Uhg…®n ne Tata r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôhatat Iesu Kristo. In Tata it…ôm in n…ôuk…ôt…®n nas…ôkitun…ôn, k…ôn in Uhg…®n it…ôm nol kep…®n…ôn rafin tat…®s…®-p…ôn ron.\x - \xo 1:3 \xt Rom 15:5 \x*  
\v 4 In tatol kep…®n kitat e n…ôrat…ôn rafin r…ôhatat m…ôm…ô kitat kot…®tun nol kep…®n…ôn net…ômim e n…ôrat…ôn p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n. K…ôn kitat kotol kep…®n ilat e nol…ôn r…ôha nol kep…®n…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômol k…ôm kitat.  
\v 5 Tahmen …ôm e nahm…ô…ôn it…ôm Kristo t…ômos, t…ômuwa m…®n e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhatat. K…ôn e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, Kristo in suat…®p m…ôm…ô nol kep…®n…ôn t…ômuwa p…®k e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhatat, k…ôn roiu nol kep…®n…ôn r…ôhatat tatuw…®n m…®n o net…ômim p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n.\x - \xo 1:5 \xt Sam 34:19 \x*  
\v 6 Ok…ôm…ô it…®mat ekoat…ôto nahm…ô…ôn, nahm…ô…ôn …ôh tatuwa ot…®mat nian ekoat…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r, k…ôn namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r …ôh otol kep…®n it…ômat mosmeg…ôh it…ômat. Ok…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ômol kep…®n it…®mat, tatol m…ôm…ô it…®mat ekot…®tun nol kep…®n…ôn it…ômat. K…ôn noan nol kep…®n…ôn …ôh, tatoe-in e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat, k…ôn nian n…ôkotat…®g e nahm…ô…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm it…ôm kitat kotat…®g lan, t…ôtasitu et…ômat m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…ôtul …ôskas…®k matuw…®n matuw…®n.  
\v 7 It…®mat emot…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn …ôskas…®k r…ôhat…®mat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn o Uhg…®n ot…ômat m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…ôtul …ôskas…®k. Tol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu kitat rafin koatat…®g e nat…®g…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm m…ôm…ô, it…ômat nakoat…ôto nahm…ô…ôn it…ôm ekoatat…®g lan, k…ôn tahmen-ahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô nakotos nol kep…®n…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm emotos.   
\p
\v 8 Piak m…®n ne w…®n…®k m…®n, ekotolkeike m…ôm…ô n…ôkot…®tun w…®r nian …ôskas…®k m…®n it…ôm emotat…®g lan e profens ik…®n Esia. N…ôrat…ôn asol m…®n k…ômotu it…®mat, tapr…ôk…®s-in n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôhat…®mat, t…ômol n…®kit…®mat t…ôht m…ôm…ô ok…ôm-naka ekot…®m…®s.\x - \xo 1:8 \xt W…ôk 19:23; 1 Kor 15:32 \x*  
\v 9 N…®pahrien…ôn, it…®mat emot…ôto m…ôm…ô k…®neg…ôhan-in r…ôk…®s it…®mat m…ôm…ô ekot…®m…®s. M…ôto nian …ôskas…®k m…®n …ôh k…ômotuwa m…ôm…ô esotag…®le…ôn et…®mat, m…ôto ekotag…®le e Uhg…®n it…ôm tatol et…ôm t…ôm…®m…®s t…ômeg…ôh m…®n.  
\v 10 In t…ômosmeg…ôh it…®mat e n…ôrat…ôn asol …ôh it…ôm t…ômatuw…®n o n…®m…®s…ôn, k…ôn in otosmeg…ôh it…®mat e n…ôrat…ôn it…ôm ot…ôpanuwa. Emot…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn …ôskas…®k r…ôhat…®mat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn lan m…ôm…ô in otosmeg…ôh m…®n it…®mat.\x - \xo 1:10 \xt 2 Tim 4:18 \x*  
\v 11 K…ôn in otol n…ôhlan nian nakot…ôfak ot…®mat m…ôm…ô, net…ômim tep…ôt okot…ônwiwi Uhg…®n o nat…®mnat w…®r it…ôm in otol k…ôm it…®mat m…ôto-inu net…ômim tep…ôt k…ômot…ôfak ot…®mat.   
\s1 Pol t…ôm…ôuhlin r…ôhan n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn o r…ôhan naliw…ôk…ôn  
\p
\v 12 Roiu ek…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u m…ôsaul…®s…ôn m…ôm…ô, e n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhat…®mat, n…®kit…®mat t…ôht m…ôm…ô esotol…ôn nat kit t…ôrat e nol…ôn r…ôhat…®mat. E nol…ôn m…®n rafin it…ôm emotol, it…®mat emot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn suat…®p it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…®t…ôpun m…ôm…ô emot…ôghat …ôtuat…®p …ôm moat…ôn …ôhag-…ôhag n…ôghat…ôn. Emotol nol…ôn …ôh k…ôm net…ôm …ôpnap…®n …ôm r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn, k…ôn motol tapr…ôk…®s k…ôm it…ômat. Esot…ôghat…ôn e n…®tun…ôn …ôm r…ôhat…®mat r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn, m…ôto emotag…®le …ôm e n…ôw…®r…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.  
\v 13-14 Iat…ôn n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu, esot…ôte…ôn n…ôghat…ôn kit it…ôm ti…ôk…®s ot…ômat o nafin…ôn, o n…®tun…ôn n…®p…ôt…®n. Roiu, n…ôkot…®tun m…ôs…®n n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhat…®mat, m…ôto iakolkeike p…®k m…ôm…ô nian kit on…ôkot…®tun rafin. K…ôn e nol…ôn …ôh, nian I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu otuwa m…®n, it…ômat on…ôkotagien ot…®mat tahmen m…®n m…ôm…ô it…®mat ekotagien ot…ômat.\x - \xo 1:13-14 \xt 2 Kor 5:12; Fil 2:16 \x*   
\p
\v 15-16 M…ôto-inu en…®tun m…ôm…ô nakotagien ot…®mat, n…®kik t…ôht m…ôm…ô nian ekatuw…®n Masetonia, ekaup…ôn m…®mn…ô m…ôplan it…ômat, k…ôn nian ek…®t…ôl…®g Masetonia, ek…®mn…ô m…®n m…ôplan it…ômat. Tol n…ôhlan, nakatos n…ôw…®r…ôn mau k…ôiu. K…ôn uaris…®g e it…ôm m…®n …ôh, on…ôkotasitu lak motahl-ip…ôn io ekuw…®n n…®t…ôn Jutia.\x - \xo 1:15-16 \xt 1 Kor 16:5-6 \x*  
\v 17 ?N…®kit…ômat t…ôht m…ôm…ô, nian emol n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn m…®n …ôh, m…ôto emol …ôpnap…®n …ôm? ?O, k…ôm-naka n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhak t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn e nol…ôn r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn, tahmen e net…ômim it…ôm koat…ôn ‚Äú…ôw…ôh‚Äù ne ‚Äúk…ôp‚Äù e n…ôghat…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm?   
\p
\v 18 It…ômat n…ôkot…®tun m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n nian rafin tatol r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn, k…ôn io m…®n, r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat s…ôn…ôm…ô, ‚Äú…ôw…ôh‚Äù ne ‚Äúk…ôp,‚Äù  
\v 19 m…ôto-inu r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn o N…ôt…® Uhg…®n Iesu Kristo, it…ôm em…ôhal…ôn-iar…ôp k…ôm it…ômat it…®m…ôhal Saelas ne Timoti, s…ôn…ôm…ô, ‚Äú…ôw…ôh‚Äù ne ‚Äúk…ôp,‚Äù m…ôto e Kristo, nian rafin r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn in ‚Äú…ôw…ôh,‚Äù in n…®pahrien…ôn.\x - \xo 1:19 \xt W…ôk 18:5 \x*  
\v 20 Tol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu, nat …ôpnap…®n n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn kuw…ôh Uhg…®n t…ômol, ilat kotuwa n…®pahrien…ôn e Kristo, inu n…ôghat…ôn ‚Äú…ôw…ôh‚Äù r…ôha Uhg…®n. Tol n…ôhlan, e Kristo, kitat koat…ôn ‚ÄúAmen, ∆èw…ôh‚Äù k…ôm Uhg…®n, k…ôn moat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…®n lan.\x - \xo 1:20 \xt Nol ∆èp…ôn 3:14 \x*  
\v 21 Uhg…®n …ôm tatol it…®mat ekoat…ôtul …ôskas…®k e Kristo kitat min it…ômat. In t…ôm…®t…ôpun kitat,  
\v 22 k…ôn t…ômol mak e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhatat m…ôm…ô kitat r…ôhan m…®n, k…ôn t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn r…ôhan Narm…®n e n…®kitat m…ôm…ô kitat okot…®tun roiu m…ôm…ô r…ôhan n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn m…®n, ilat rafin okotuwa n…®pahrien…ôn e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhatat o nian kit.\x - \xo 1:22 \xt 2 Kor 5:5; Efes 1:13-14 \x*   
\p
\v 23 K…ôn roiu, ok…ôm…ô es…ôn…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn, p…ôs Uhg…®n otol nalp…®n…ôn k…ôm io. Em…ôsuwam…ôn Korin m…ôto-inu esolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô ek…ôn n…ôghat…ôn …ôskas…®k kit k…ôm it…ômat.  
\v 24 Esotolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô ekot…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhat…ômat, k…ôp. M…ôto ekotol w…ôk kitat min it…ômat o nagien…ôn r…ôhat…ômat, m…ôto-inu it…ômat n…®noat…ôtul …ôskas…®k r…ôk…®s e nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhat…ômat.\x - \xo 1:24 \xt 1 Pita 5:3 \x*   
\c 2  
\m
\v 1 Tol n…ôhlan, en…ôn r…ôk…®s e n…®kik m…ôm…ô okol es…®mn…ô m…®n…ôn m…ôplan it…ômat mol n…®kit…ômat tahm…ô.\x - \xo 2:1 \xt 1 Kor 4:21 \x*  
\v 2 ?Em…ôn n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu, ok…ôm…ô ekol n…®kit…ômat tahm…ô, pah u ik…®n-un otol io n…®kik tagien? It…ômat …ôm, it…ôm emol n…®kit…ômat tahm…ô.  
\v 3 K…ôn em…ôte naoa …ôh, m…ôm…ô nian ek…®mn…ô, es…ôto…ôn t…ôrat e n…®kik. Esolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô net…ômim it…ôm okot…ôk…ôike motol n…®kik tagien, ilat okotol m…ôm…ô ek…ôto t…ôrat. Em…ôte naoa …ôh e nol…ôn …ôh, m…ôto-inu en…®tun m…ôm…ô kitat kiti…ôh …ôm, k…ôn nian n…®kik tagien, k…ôn n…®kit…ômat m…®n tagien.  
\v 4 Tol n…ôhlan, nian em…ôte naoa …ôh k…ôm it…ômat, n…®kik t…ôpou p…®k ot…ômat, k…ôn n…®kik t…®t…ôg…®t, nahui n…ômt…ôk tai…ôh ot…ômat. Es…ôte…ôn naoa …ôh m…ôm…ô otol n…®kit…ômat t…ôpou, m…ôto em…ôte m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…®tun r…ôhak nolkeike…ôn asol ot…ômat.\x - \xo 2:4 \xt W…ôk 20:31 \x*   
\s1 Aluin nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôha nol t…ôfag…ô  
\p
\v 5 Et…ômim it…ôm t…ômol n…ôrat…ôn, t…ômol io ek…ôto t…ôrat, m…ôto t…ômol it…ômat rafin nakot…ôto t…ôrat p…®k, m…ôto esolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhak e nat u in t…ôskas…®k p…®k.  
\v 6 Nalp…®n…ôn it…ôm it…ômat tep…ôt n…ômotos-ip…ôn k…ôm in t…®nahmen.  
\v 7 M…ôto roiu …ôh, n…ôkot…ôk…ôike motaluin r…ôhan nol…ôn rat k…ôn motol-w…®r n…®kin, m…ôm…ô n…®kin ot…ôs…ôpou p…®k…ôn mol t…ôme e r…ôhan n…ômeg…ôh…ôn.  
\v 8 Iat…ôtap…ôh …ôskas…®k ot…ômat m…ôm…ô nakotuw…®n motol t…ôw…®r k…ôm in m…ôm…ô in ot…®tun r…ôhat…ômat nolkeike…ôn ron.  
\v 9 Em…ôte naoa …ôh k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô ek…ôplan m…ôm…ô on…ôkotol n…ôwiak e nat…®mnat rafin, o k…ôp.  
\v 10 Ok…ôm…ô it…ômat n…ôkotaluin nol…ôn rat r…ôha suah kit, io m…®n ekaluin r…ôhan nol…ôn. Ok…ôm…ô suah …ôh t…ômol nat t…ôrat neen m…ôm…ô io ek…ôk…ôike maluin r…ôhan nol…ôn, m…ôto enaluin r…ôk…®s r…ôhan nol…ôn e n…®gan…ômt…® Kristo. Emol n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô otasitu et…ômat  
\v 11 m…ôm…ô Setan ot…ôs…ôr…ôk…®n…ôn kitat e r…ôhan neiueiu…ô…ôn m…®n, m…ôto-inu kitat kot…®tun r…ôk…®s r…ôhan n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn o nol…ôn n…ôrat…ôn.\x - \xo 2:11 \xt Luk 22:31 \x*   
\s1 Net…ômim it…ôm koat…ôn-iar…ôp  //  namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r  
\p
\v 12 Nian emuw…®n …ôp…ôh Troas o n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r r…ôha Kristo, em…ôplan m…ôm…ô I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ômol suat…®p k…ôm io.\x - \xo 2:12 \xt W…ôk 14:27; 1 Kor 16:9 \x*  
\v 13 M…ôto esat…®g …ôm…ôlinu…ôn e r…ôhak n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn m…ôto-inu, em…ôs…ôplan…ôn piak Taetas ik…®n …ôh. K…ôn emauiat…®pin ilat, miet muw…®n Masetonia.\x - \xo 2:13 \xt W…ôk 20:1 \x*   
\p
\v 14 P…ôs kot…ônwiwi Uhg…®n, m…ôto-inu in t…ômol win e r…ôhan t…®k…®m…®r m…®n e n…ôluag…®n…ôn. K…ôn tahmen e kig kit it…ôm t…ômol win e n…ôluag…®n…ôn m…®nat…®t…ôl…®g matit r…ôhan mopael m…®n ne r…ôhan t…®k…®m…®r m…®n, Uhg…®n tatit it…®mat e Kristo. K…ôn it…®mat r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim it…ôm ioat…ôn-iar…ôp nenat…®g…ôn r…ôha Kristo, k…ôn nenat…®g…ôn …ôh in tahmen e n…ômi…ôw…®n kit it…ôm tatuw…®n ik…®n p…®s…®n-p…®s…®n m…®n.  
\v 15 E n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n, it…®mat ekotahmen e n…ômi…ôw…®n r…ôha Kristo k…ôm net…ômim rafin, net…ômim it…ôm Uhg…®n tatosmeg…ôh ilat, ne net…ômim it…ôm okotuw…®n e nalp…®n…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.  
\v 16 It…®mat n…ômi…ôw…®n r…ôha n…®m…®s…ôn k…ôm neen it…ôm tat…ôg…ôtun ilat m…ôm…ô okot…®m…®s. K…ôn it…®mat n…ômi…ôw…®n r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn k…ôm neen, it…ôm tat…ôg…ôtun ilat m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n otosmeg…ôh ilat. ?K…ôn pah u t…®tun nol…ôn w…ôk asol …ôh?\x - \xo 2:16 \xt Luk 2:34; 2 Kor 3:5-6 \x*  
\v 17 M…ôto it…®mat esotahmen…ôn e net…ôm …ôpnap…®n m…®n, it…ôm koat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n o nos …ôm…ôn m…ôni. K…ôp, m…ôto Uhg…®n t…ômahl-ip…ôn it…®mat, k…ôn e Kristo, it…®mat ekot…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n, k…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhat…®mat t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn e n…®kit…®mat it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p …ôm.   
\c 3  
\m
\v 1 Ok…ôm…ô naka n…®kit…ômat t…ôht m…ôm…ô enoat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr it…®mat m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkoteg…ôhan lan. Net…ômim neen okot…ôk…ôike motos naoa kit it…ôm k…ôm…ôte elat nian koatuw…®n o net…ôm kot…ôruru ilat. ?Tahro n…®kit…ômat t…ôht m…ôm…ô suah kit ot…ôk…ôike m…ôte naoa n…ôhlan et…®mat k…ôm it…ômat? ?O, tahro it…ômat …ôm nakotolkeike m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…ôte? !K…ôp!\x - \xo 3:1 \xt W…ôk 18:27; 2 Kor 5:12 \x*  
\v 2 It…ômat at…®p …ôm n…ôkotahmen e naoa it…ôm tatol …ôp w…ôk r…ôhat…®mat. Naoa …ôh k…ôm…ôte-p…ôn e n…®kit…®mat, it…ôm net…ômim rafin koatafin k…ôn moat…®tun.\x - \xo 3:2 \xt 1 Kor 9:2 \x*  
\v 3 It…ômat noa r…ôha w…ôk r…ôhat…®mat. K…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô it…ômat naoa k…ôtafin it…ôm Kristo t…ôm…ôte. Kristo t…ôm…ôte naoa …ôh e Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm tat…ômeg…ôh, m…ôto t…ôs…ôte…ôn e nelm…® et…ômim. K…ôn in t…ôm…ôs…ôte-p…ôn…ôn e k…ôpiel epin-epin, m…ôto t…ôm…ôte-p…ôn e n…®ki net…ômim.\f + \fr 3:3 \ft Nian Pol tat…ôghat e n…ôghat…ôn ‚Äúk…ôm…ôs…ôte-p…ôn…ôn e k…ôpiel epin-epin,‚Äù tat…ôghat e Lou it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn k…ôm Moses, k…ôn Moses t…ôm…ôte e k…ôpiel.\f*\x - \xo 3:3 \xt Eks 24:12; Jer 31:33; Esik 36:26-27 \x*   
\p
\v 4 It…®mat esot…ôg…®n…ôn o n…ôn…ôn n…ôhlan ot…ômat m…ôto-inu it…®mat ioatat…®g e Kristo, k…ôn moatahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n.\x - \xo 3:4 \xt W…ôk 20:31 \x*  
