\v 21 Iat…ôg…®n m…ôm…ô nian ek…®mn…ô m…®n, r…ôhak Uhg…®n ot…®l…ôs-i…ôhau io e n…®gan…ômt…®t…ômat, k…ôn n…®kik ot…®t…ôg…®t k…ôn ekas…ôk ot…ômat neen it…ôm n…ômotol nol…ôn rat aup…ôn, k…ôn m…ôsot…ôuhlin…ôn ilat o nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhalat it…ôm koatol nian rafin, inu koatol nol…ôn rat it…ôm tol naul…®s…ôn o n…ôn…ôn, k…ôn n…ôman ne n…®p…®tan koatan anion, k…ôn koatol n…ôhlan …ôpnap…®n …ôm.\x - \xo 12:21 \xt 2 Kor 13:2 \x*   
